newsitem.title: SINGAPORE: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Oct 7.
newsitem.headline: Singapore bunker final report and prices- Oct 7.

text.p: DELIVERED U.S.$/TONNE) 380 CST 180 CST MDO GAS OIL

COMMENTS - Singapore bunker prices ended a shade lower on Monday amid a quiet market despite stable cargo prices, traders said. Bunker 380-cst were quoted at $119-$122 per tonne, 180-cst supplies were indicated at $114-$118. Trades said the market was lacklustre. MDO prices were quoted between $212 and $218 and gas oil was steady at $230-$235.
